Release Notes
=============

Here you can see the full list of changes between AMQPeek versions. Versions
are in form of *headline.major.minor* numbers. Backwards-compatible changes
increment the minor version number only.

Version 0.0.4
-------------

Released 2017-05-28

* Added `queue_limits` configuration. This allow queues to
  be defined by groupling them by limits

Version 0.0.3
-------------

Released 2017-05-07

* Correct generate config message with correct command
* Add passive connection to queues, allowing us to drop queue settings from config
* Add notification, sent when queue has not been declared

Version 0.0.2
-------------

Released 2016-10-30

* Config file no longer added to home directory on install
* Config generated on demand
* Default config location changed to current working directory
* Other tidy ups

Version 0.0.1
-------------

Released 2016-10-11

* Initial release
